lore:
This card's effects cannot be negated. If a "Honest-Eyes Cloud Sheep" is destroyed and sent to your Graveyard: You can Special Summon this card from your hand or Graveyard. This card's Normal Summon cannot be negated. Unaffected by your opponent's card effects. Cannot be destroyed by battle. During damage calculation, when you are about to take 5000 or more battle damage: Gain 5000 Life Points first, also you take no damage from that battle. If a monster you control is destroyed by battle and sent to the Graveyard: Special Summon it in Attack Position, also double its ATK. Once per turn, (Quick Effect): You can activate 1 of these effects;
●Target 1 other face-up card you control; place 1 Guard Counter on it. If it would ever be destroyed, remove the counter instead.
●1 monster you control gains 5000 ATK, except "Honest-Eyes Thunders of War".
